data.description: BEAUTIFULL HOUSE!!!!  The house for somebody you love!!!  Very clean, spotless clean, neat, homy, spacy, with a lot of updates in quiet neighborhood.   Big and spacy patio, nice either backyard and front yard, sidewalk, trees,...    Sorry, House rule, NO shoes inside the house, please take off shoes or use boots.    Renovated at 2011 before current owner bought it, but re-renovated again thru years. owner is handy man.  A lot updates done thru years, not prepared for sale. roof, wood floors, windows, cabinets, granite countertops, built in oven, updated garage, patio, bathrooms, shed, drain system, electric control panel replaces and added generator for electricity,....      Cannot find batter house in area. Price reflects quality.
